I like the most.

26:08.833 --> 26:12.066
It's that love line
in your socket.

26:15.333 --> 26:18.933
I only have eyes for you.

27:40.900 --> 27:42.333
"My darling Gregory.

27:42.400 --> 27:45.266
"I know this is dangerous,
but I cannot help myself.

27:45.333 --> 27:48.300
"I simply had to tell you
how very much I love you.

27:48.366 --> 27:50.133
"My heart is bursting.

27:50.200 --> 27:52.233
