27:54.066 --> 27:56.400
"We must be together somehow.

27:56.466 --> 27:59.566
"If I cannot be with you,
I fear I will die.

27:59.633 --> 28:01.500
Your loving Jane."

30:35.500 --> 30:37.000
Gregory.

30:37.800 --> 30:39.833
Are you still here?

31:45.000 --> 31:47.933
I was dusting
and I found this loose panel.

31:48.000 --> 31:51.766
The panel fell off
and there they were.

31:51.833 --> 31:54.366
It's amazing.

31:54.433 --> 31:56.533
Who were they from?

31:56.600 --> 32:00.433
Someone named Jane
to someone named Gregory.

32:00.500 --> 32:02.266
They're incredible.

32:02.333 --> 32:05.433
They're beyond romantic.

32:05.500 --> 32:07.766
Jane was Gregory's mistress.

32:07.833 --> 32:09.566
- His mistress?
- Mm-hmm.

32:09.633 --> 32:10.933
Hoo-hoo!

32:11.000 --> 32:12.600
Sounds wicked.

32:14.033 --> 32:16.066
But what about the wife?

32:16.133 --> 32:18.566
I've been up
all night reading these.

32:18.633 --> 32:22.133
Jane and Gregory really loved
each other heart and soul.

32:22.200 --> 32:23.833
Do you have any idea
who they were?

32:23.900 --> 32:27.533
Not a clue. I've been
living here for 30 years.

32:27.600 --> 32:31.000
Never heard of any Gregory
or any Jane.

32:31.066 --> 32:32.866
Any idea when this apartment
house was built?

32:32.933 --> 32:35.300
Hmm, 1890 I think. It..

32:35.366 --> 32:38.300
That's what I was always told.

32:38.366 --> 32:42.666
This was Springwood's
first high-rise.

32:42.733 --> 32:45.633
You know, these apartments
used to be a lot larger.

32:45.700 --> 32:48.833
Yours and mine
used to be one apartment.

32:53.033 --> 32:56.433
What must have gone
on here before..

32:56.500 --> 32:58.733
...within these walls?

33:44.433 --> 33:46.166
"Darling, I'm afraid

33:44.433 --> 33:46.166
there's something

33:46.233 --> 33:47.600
"we must face together.

33:47.666 --> 33:50.166
"Something that threatens
to tear us apart.

33:50.233 --> 33:52.800
I fear that Margaret
has become suspicious of us."

34:12.966 --> 34:16.033
Have I told you before
how very much I love you?

35:13.833 --> 35:16.466
The letters are getting
more and more intense.

35:16.533 --> 35:19.000
Gregory is more
passionate than ever.

35:19.066 --> 35:22.800
He says he can't live
without Jane.

35:22.866 --> 35:25.233
But Gregory's wife Margare

35:25.300 --> 35:28.233
is starting to get suspicious.

35:28.300 --> 35:31.000
She's even spying on us.

35:31.066 --> 35:32.200
Us?

35:33.100 --> 35:35.500
Did I say us?

35:35.566 --> 35:37.266
I was thinking
of rearranging the furniture

35:37.333 --> 35:39.300
to the way it was
when Gregory lived here.

35:39.366 --> 35:41.000
'How could you do that?'

35:41.066 --> 35:43.533
'Do the letters
have floor plans?'

35:43.600 --> 35:45.033
Hmm. Kind of.

35:47.200 --> 35:50.666
They made love in almost
every room of the house.

35:50.733 --> 35:53.100
'You've been
holding back on me.'

35:53.166 --> 35:56.200
You didn't tell me
there were any good parts.

35:56.266 --> 35:57.733
Oh, there are.

35:59.366 --> 36:02.566
There are some very good parts.

36:02.633 --> 36:05.433
Well, how did he pull that off?

36:05.500 --> 36:09.533
Where was the wife while the two
of them were screwing around?

36:09.600 --> 36:12.866
Well, sometimes at tea parties.

36:12.933 --> 36:16.333
Sometimes at their house
in the country.

36:16.400 --> 36:18.700
It was all planned
very carefully.

36:21.533 --> 36:23.500
Gregory thought of everything.

36:49.300 --> 36:51.633
I didn't scare you, did I?

36:51.700 --> 36:54.300
Oh, you're strange.
Anybody ever tell you that

36:54.366 --> 36:56.700
I've been thinking about you.

36:56.766 --> 36:58.800
And I want you
to go out with me.

36:58.866 --> 37:01.400
Nothing personal.
But I'm not interested.

37:03.633 --> 37:06.533
Come on. You're not that busy.

37:06.600 --> 37:08.033
What about tonight?

37:10.333 --> 37:12.866
Aren't you interested
in a real man?

37:12.933 --> 37:14.933
I've got a date.

37:22.133 --> 37:24.300
"My darling..

37:24.366 --> 37:27.233
"...I want to be
in your arms again

37:27.300 --> 37:30.100
"to feel your mouth on mine

37:30.166 --> 37:32.100
and hear your whisper."

37:46.566 --> 37:49.066
I love you.

37:49.133 --> 37:52.000
I wanna be in your arms again..

37:52.066 --> 37:54.500
...to feel your mouth on mine.

38:05.000 --> 38:07.033
To know your touch.

38:08.333 --> 38:10.100
Oh, to kiss.

39:45.933 --> 39:47.000
He's mine!

39:58.533 --> 40:01.666
So...what's the latest?

40:01.733 --> 40:05.433
And this time,
tell me the good stuff first.

40:05.500 --> 40:07.400
I don't wanna talk about
the letters anymore.

40:07.466 --> 40:10.466
They're making you lonely?

40:10.533 --> 40:13.033
What's more romantic?

40:13.100 --> 40:15.733
Bein' the wife
or-or bein' the other woman?

40:15.800 --> 40:17.200
Oh! That's easy.

40:17.266 --> 40:19.100
The other woman.

40:19.166 --> 40:21.300
She only sees
the best parts of him.

40:21.366 --> 40:23.300
Shouldn't be that way.

40:24.500 --> 40:26.300
'Dream on, sweetie.'

40:26.366 --> 40:28.100
No. No, I'm finished with him.

40:28.166 --> 40:29.366
Done.

40:29.433 --> 40:31.300
What happened?

40:32.166 --> 40:33.966
He didn't dump her, did he?

40:34.033 --> 40:36.766
No. No, he didn't.

40:39.300 --> 40:42.200
Jane was...exciting.

40:42.266 --> 40:44.500
Impetuous, romantic.

40:44.566 --> 40:46.966
'She'd risk anything for him.'

40:47.033 --> 40:49.733
She was the perfect mistress.

40:49.800 --> 40:51.533
But Margret..

40:51.600 --> 40:53.666
...she loved him.

40:53.733 --> 40:55.700
Supported him.

40:57.233 --> 41:00.400
But she wasn't enough.

41:00.466 --> 41:02.500
But she was his wife.

41:05.000 --> 41:06.566
I don't wanna talk
about this anymore.

41:06.633 --> 41:08.233
Okay? I just..
It's over.

41:08.300 --> 41:10.100
It's finished.

41:34.700 --> 41:37.200
Look, I don't understand.
What is wrong with me?

41:37.266 --> 41:38.200
What?

41:38.266 --> 41:39.733
All I want to do is go out

41:39.800 --> 41:41.033
What's wrong with that?

41:41.100 --> 41:42.900
Nothing. Really, it's..

41:42.966 --> 41:45.000
It's just I'm involved.

41:45.066 --> 41:46.433
You don't sound too sure
about that.

41:46.500 --> 41:48.333
I don't think you know
what you want.

41:48.400 --> 41:50.333
No, I do.

41:52.733 --> 41:54.666
What? A-a guy
has got to be perfect.

41:54.733 --> 41:57.300
Or you're not interested.
Is that it?

41:57.366 --> 41:58.800
What's wrong with perfect?

41:58.866 --> 42:00.966
It doesn't exists.

42:01.033 --> 42:04.033
Well, I can find it.

42:10.466 --> 42:12.600
I hope you like yourself

42:12.666 --> 42:14.100
because with an attitude
like that

42:14.166 --> 42:17.466
you're gonna be alone
for a long time.

42:54.566 --> 42:56.233
Oh, no.

42:59.400 --> 43:02.266
Oh, I don't wanna be here.

43:02.333 --> 43:04.500
I don't wanna be in this dream.

43:11.333 --> 43:13.533
Do you know how much I hate you?

43:13.600 --> 43:15.766
How much I despise you?

43:15.833 --> 43:17.233
I'm sorry, I never thought--

43:17.300 --> 43:19.133
I won't let you come between us.

43:19.200 --> 43:21.533
He means too much to me.

43:21.600 --> 43:23.466
There's no reason for this.
It's over.

43:23.533 --> 43:25.400
Do you think I'm that stupid?

43:25.466 --> 43:27.433
Do you think I can't see
straight through you?

43:27.500 --> 43:28.800
I don't wanna destroy
what you have.

43:28.866 --> 43:30.300
I have my own life to lead.

43:30.366 --> 43:33.400
You don't deserve
a man like Gregory.

43:39.266 --> 43:41.266
Oh, Gregory,
thank God you're here.

43:41.333 --> 43:44.666
I'm sorry it had
to be this way, Margret.

43:44.733 --> 43:47.633
Margret? But I'm Jane.

43:47.700 --> 43:50.533
No. You're nothing like Jane.

43:50.600 --> 43:51.733
You don't know me.

43:51.800 --> 43:53.933
You've never seen me before.

43:58.233 --> 43:59.533
It's red.

44:01.000 --> 44:02.966
My hair...it's not red.

44:03.033 --> 44:05.700
- 'Of course it is, Margret.'
- It can't be.

44:05.766 --> 44:08.666
We've fallen in love,
Jane and I.

44:08.733 --> 44:10.900
And we can't be together
if I'm married to you.

44:10.966 --> 44:12.933
Oh, Gregory.

44:13.800 --> 44:17.300
I wish I didn't have to do this.

44:17.366 --> 44:20.200
But I really have no choice.

44:20.266 --> 44:22.200
I don't understand.

44:22.266 --> 44:24.500
I was Jane.

44:24.566 --> 44:26.533
Iwas

44:29.666 --> 44:31.600
Aah!

44:33.766 --> 44:34.733
Aah!

44:49.200 --> 44:52.633
Next time you're alone
in your house

44:52.700 --> 44:55.433
think about who went before you.

44:55.500 --> 44:57.933
It might be pretty crowded.

44:58.000 --> 45:00.500
The dead have to go somewhere.

45:02.566 --> 45:03.966
Aah!

45:04.033 --> 45:06.866
